{"tid":1434542,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民間暗花制衡克警","createTime":"2019-08-08T20:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T18:22:49.000Z","uid":283811,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea963ea639fe1bc0cc5f8c71f9d6e9f8085ef27","tid":1434542,"uid":283811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:47:42.000Z","msg":"（集思廣益）<br />\n689可以出百萬懸紅，市民都一樣可以<br />\n眾籌方式對提供有力證據告犯法警員<br />\n任何罪行都可以，成功入罪，以每年一萬計奬金，設上下限<br />\n<br />\n有效打擊及改善警員犯案數字<br />\n增加警員間互相警剔及監察之效<br />\n間接推動香港私家偵探行業<br />\n提升警隊形象<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對舉報者身分保密，歡迎警員舉報！"},{"pid":"17c407c1036a94f25e4f952208ea3bffa5780fc6","tid":1434542,"uid":295273,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:39:48.000Z","msg":"舉報者身分保密？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁點知整暗花嗰個普通市民唔係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f3f13796441216ca9a3fd66ace14a712c30cfb","tid":1434542,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T22:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5XqWt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5XqWt.png&h=2edd738f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dw1Dapa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDw1Dapa.jpg&h=f1f6aa56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQGGSEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQGGSEb.jpg&h=f8cc4264&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKDJ5X5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKDJ5X5.jpg&h=efb6ebbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOSKQpb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOSKQpb.jpg&h=e6dcca84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cm36bK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcm36bK9.jpg&h=5ce2c060&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aeb40f0